@xijinpingzuzong I was very careless in my comment, sorry
I think compared to those who tore down billboards, those who came out to protest were also exercising their rights in a civilized manner
Since they love Chinese culture, it is also brave for them to stand up to defend the Chinese New Year. For these young people, this is the beginning of participation, and then they will exercise such rights when they encounter something they think they should stand up for in the future. I am very optimistic
